他所囚禁的生灵围绕在他身旁，使身边敌方单位每秒都受到伤害，但会迅速消耗自己的魔力。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">关闭： </span>当卡尔瑟斯击杀一个单位，他将回复 {{ e2 }} 点魔力。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">开启： </span>消耗 {{ cost }} 点魔力对附近敌方单位造成每秒 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"color99FF99\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 点魔法伤害。 ","leveltip":{"label":["每秒伤害","回复魔力","每秒消耗魔力"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"," {{ e2 }} -> {{ e2NL }}","{{ cost }} -> {{ costnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5],"cooldownBurn":"0.5","cost":[30,42,54,66,78],"costBurn":"30/42/54/66/78","effect":[null,[30,50,70,90,110],[20,27,34,41,48],[0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5,0.5]],"effectBurn":[null,"30/50/70/90/110","20/27/34/41/48","0.5"],"vars":[{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.2,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"ManaPerSecond","range":[550,550,550,550,550],"rangeBurn":"550","image":{"full":"KarthusDefile.png","sprite":"spell13.png","group":"spell","x":432,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }} 每秒消耗魔力 "},{"id":"KarthusFallenOne","name":"安魂曲","description":"在吟唱安魂曲持续 3 秒后，卡尔瑟斯将会对所有敌方英雄造成伤害。","tooltip":"吟唱 3 秒后，卡尔瑟斯对所有敌方英雄造成 {{ e1 }} <span class=\"color99FF99\">（+{{ a1 }}）</span> 点魔法伤害（无视距离远近）。 ","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","消耗魔力t","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"," {{ cost }} -> {{ costnNL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[200,180,160],"cooldownBurn":"200/180/160","cost":[150,175,200],"costBurn":"150/175/200","effect":[null,[250,400,550],[200,300,400]],"effectBurn":[null,"250/400/550","200/300/400"],"vars":[{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.6,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":"self","rangeBurn":"self","image":{"full":"KarthusFallenOne.png","sprite":"spell13.png","group":"spell","x":0,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }} 魔力"}],"passive":{"name":"死亡契约","description":"死亡后卡尔瑟斯进入灵体状态，可以继续施法，持续 7 秒。","image":{"full":"Karthus_Passive.png","sprite":"passive4.png","group":"passive","x":336,"y":0,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[{"champion":"Karthus","title":"KarthusDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ASCENSION","priority":